title: Aquila Post #1
author: Nahubi
pages:
#- THE AQUILA POST§0
§0Issue 1§0
§0February 18, 2017§0
§0
§0§lAquila Convicts First Criminal§0
§0§oBy Nahubi§0
§0
§0Around 9PM Central Time last night (2/17), Aquila officially convicted it's first criminal of crimes. 
#- Pugggles, who had been a resident for roughly 2 or 3 days before the incidents, was found guilty of three counts of theft and four counts of breaking and entering after pleading guilty. §0
§0
§0Gjum, §0§oChief Justice of Aquila§0, sentenced Puggles to:
#- three days of exile pearling in addition to the two days he had already served;§0
§0Banishment from Aquila and it's territories for two weeks effective immediately;§0
§0and reparations in full to all victims.§0
§0
§0The crime was first reported several days earlier by 
#- new resident of Aquila, Nahubi, who found Pugggles attempting to crack a chest in his neighbor's house, and caught the illegal entrance on his snitch.§0
§0
§0Could this mean a new wave of crime in Aquila? It will remain to be seen.
#- §l§oHave a hot scoop for the Aquila Post? Contact Nahubi ingame, on Discord, or on reddit at /u/Azhf!§0
§0
